textfsm_template:
Value PLATFORM (\S+)
Value MODEL (.*)
Value SERIAL (.*)
Value SLOT (\d)
Value DESCR (.*)
Value LOM_STATUS (\S+)
Value LOM_REV (\S+)
 
 
Start
  ^Platform:\s${PLATFORM}
  ^Model:\s${MODEL}
  ^Serial Number:\s${SERIAL} -> Record
  ^LOM\sStatus:\s${LOM_STATUS}
  ^LOM\sFirmware\sRevision:\s${LOM_REV} -> Record
  ^Line\scard\s${SLOT}\smodel:\s${MODEL}
  ^Line\scard\s${SLOT}\stype:\s${DESCR} -> Record
